other_tests.findings: Multiple cystic tumors were excised from the scalp, face, right shoulder, and right thigh.
Microscopic examination showed different histopathologic features depending on the biopsy site, including trichilemmal cysts and discrete acanthosis with papillomatosis.
Serum 25-hydroxycholecalciferol was low prior to supplementation; levels normalized within 3 weeks after oral supplementation.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Serum 25-OH-D normalized after 3 weeks of supplementation.
